    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements for this Class III VAD hemolysis prediction application. Seven factors were formally assessed; six remain as documented epistemic gaps. Despite achieved levels falling below required levels across all assessed factors, the submission is accepted under the Minimal profile with the understanding that gap closure activities will be completed prior to regulatory submission. Monte Carlo UQ has been initiated and provides a partial basis for uncertainty characterization.",
